text: Osama Al Saleem (, born 20 August 1996) is a Saudi Arabian professional footballer who plays as a left back for Al-Khaleej . ==Career== Al-Saleem began his career at the youth team of Al-Ettifaq. He played his first match against Al-Shabab . On 9 January 2019, Al-Saleem joined side Al-Kawkab on loan for the 2018–19 season .
